libnserial (1.1.2-0ubuntu1~xenial1) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Abort pin monitoring for devices that don't support it
  * Fix race condition when checking/aborting modem events
  * Properly handle errors from pthreads
  * Treat EINTR as a non-fatal interrupt

 -- Jason Curl <jcurl@arcor.de>  Sun, 04 Jun 2017 20:46:22 +0200

